http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1834817.mkv&play_token=XoQFWm5ppw&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/yy2dmnBlPhx21GUMUJUPxA9QUFp.jpg" group-title="|ES| TERROR/SUSPENSE" tvg-type="movie" description="1901, South Africa. As the Second Anglo-Boer War rages on, a wounded General seeks refuge in the small home of a woman and her young daughter. As the hurt man settles in, he begins noticing that something is off about the two women, particularly the daughter, and before long, he’ll learn the real reason for why they’ve invited him and for how they’ve survived on their own for so long." year="2023-10-18" director="Jaco Bouwer" actors="Michele Burgers, Sven Ruygrok, Jamie-Lee Money, Lionel Newton",Breathing In (2023)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1830397.mkv&play_token=GduGeBmNIj&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/fRzhUijVlR4M545TsBRy99yZil9.jpg" group-title="|ES| TERROR/SUSPENSE" tvg-type="movie" description="After a father is given recordings from a mysterious stranger, he starts to receive communications from his deceased daughter. While he tries to decipher the messages, he starts to suspect that his support group has ulterior motives." year="2023-03-07" director="Kenny Yates" actors="Scott Hamm Duenas, Kipp Tribble, Alison Haislip, Tobin Bell, Nija Okoro",ReBroken (2023)
