#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/muIaHotSaSUQr0KZCIJOYQEe7y2.jpg" group-title="|FR| ANIMATION" tvg-type="movie" description="This time, the rivals team up to help a cowgirl and her brother save their homestead from a greedy land-grabber, and they’re going to need some help! Jerry’s three precocious nephews are all ready for action, and Tom is rounding up a posse of prairie dogs. But can a ragtag band of varmints defeat a deceitful desperado determined to deceive a damsel in distress? No matter what happens with Tom and Jerry in the saddle, it’ll be a rootin’ tootin’ good time!" year="2022-01-24" director="Warner Bros. Animation" actors="N/A",FR - Tom and Jerry Cowboy Up!  (2022)
